=== 戒煙 ===
在戒烟方面，催眠疗法比其他預防及治療措施，在治療六個月後的成功戒烟率更高。 <ref name="Cochrane2005">{{Cite journal|title=Hypnotherapy for smoking cessation|url=https://ora.ox.ac.uk/objects/uuid:f8ad59f1-8e99-47f0-adfc-79e6b149e6a4|last=Abbot|first=NC|last2=Stead|first2=LF|journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|issue=2|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD001008|year=2005|page=CD001008|pmid=10796583|last3=White|first3=AR|last4=Barnes|first4=J|editor=Jo}}</ref>

